_sText:
Surf_Tronic 

by Sangre Nueva

Skill Surf Map

made for 66tick

Map Includes:

- 1 Long Surf Stage
- 1 extra Level
- 1 Regular Jail
- 1 Endjail

Fall- retry system:

Every player has 20 tries at the beginning

After 20 Fails you get teleported to an extra Stage,

Beat the extra Stage to get another 5 tries..

Round- Timer: 4,5 Minutes:

Is the Time up players get teleported to the regular Jail 
where you can play Airhockey

The Endjail has 3 buttons for the punishment

Enjoy the Map

-Sangre

No Jail Version for Speed Surf Serve:

http://www.sendspace.com/file/on80ju
